# Day 5 Progress 🚀

## Project Built

### Lead Capture & Qualification System

## Project Summary

Built a fully automated lead management workflow using n8n, Google Sheets, and Gmail.

## Workflow

1. A new lead is added to Google Sheets
2. Google Sheets Trigger detects the new row
3. IF node checks the lead budget
4. If Budget > ₹50,000:

   * Lead is added to High Value Leads sheet
   * Automated email is sent
5. If Budget ≤ ₹50,000:

   * Lead is added to Low Value Leads sheet

## Tools Used

* n8n
* Google Sheets Trigger
* IF Node
* Google Sheets (Append Row)
* Gmail Node
* Google OAuth
* Gmail API

## Skills Learned

* Workflow automation
* Trigger-based systems
* Conditional logic
* Google integrations
* API connections
* Automated email systems
* OAuth authentication
* Data flow between nodes

## Final Result

Created a fully working Lead Capture & Qualification System that automatically categorizes leads and follows up with high-value prospects without manual effort.

## Portfolio Description

Built an automated Lead Capture & Qualification System in n8n that classifies leads based on budget, stores them in separate Google Sheets, and automatically sends emails to high-value leads. 🚀

